[00:56.80]So let me tell you a little bit about my research.
[01:01.50]My interest started about six years ago.
[01:05.20]I stumbled onto something that completely changed my life.
[01:10.80]What I found was that connection is why we're here.
[01:16.50]It's what gives purpose and meaning to our lives.
[01:20.20]This is what it's all about.
[01:23.80]It doesn't matter whether you talk to people
